# GraphXY
 
 *GraphXY* is a simple application where you can see graphs of functions of two variables. You can also compute a gradient descend/ascend on the function. 
 
Press `h` for help. Feel free to download the program below.

![**GraphXY** app video](https://youtu.be/cjhTs1DJ4-k)

